---
// src/pages/about.astro
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  altLangHref="/fr/about"
  title="About - Killian Perzo"
  description="Learn about my journey: Data Scientist specialized in Agentic AI at Median Technologies. Expert in multi-agent systems, LangChain, LangGraph. Creator of DataSentinel AI and DataBad."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-8 sm:py-16 px-4 sm:px-0">
    <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6">About</h1>

    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 leading-relaxed mb-4 sm:mb-6">
      Hi, I'm <strong>Killian</strong> — Data Scientist passionate about <span class="text-gold font-semibold">Agentic AI</span>, <span class="text-gold font-semibold">multi-agent systems</span>, and <span class="text-gold font-semibold">building autonomous agents</span>.
    </p>

    <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-3 sm:mb-4">
      After studying Sports Science (STAPS) and completing a Bachelor's in Data Science, I pursued a Master's in Data Analysis, which I will finish by the end of 2025. I currently work at <strong class="text-charcoal dark:text-white">Median Technologies</strong>, where I've developed intelligent automation solutions and AI applied to medical imaging.
    </p>

    <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-3 sm:mb-4">
      My specialty: designing <strong class="text-charcoal dark:text-white">intelligent autonomous agents</strong> capable of reasoning, collaborating, and executing complex tasks. I use frameworks like <strong class="text-charcoal dark:text-white">LangChain</strong>, <strong class="text-charcoal dark:text-white">LangGraph</strong>, and advanced LLMs (Claude, GPT) to build RAG systems, multi-agent workflows, and intelligent automation tools.
    </p>

    <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-3 sm:mb-4">
      On the personal side, I created <strong class="text-charcoal dark:text-white">DataSentinel AI</strong> — an intelligent monitoring system using autonomous agents to analyze and monitor data pipelines. I'm also developing <strong class="text-charcoal dark:text-white">Data Quality Agent</strong>, a specialized agent for automated data quality analysis with intelligent report generation.
    </p>

    <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6 sm:mb-8">
      My goal? To build AI agents that augment human intelligence and automate complex tasks. I'm looking for opportunities to develop high-impact agentic AI systems, where agent autonomy enables solving real-world problems at scale.
    </p>

    <a href="/en/contact" class="inline-block w-full sm:w-auto text-center bg-gold text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-oldgold transition active:scale-95 font-medium">
      Contact me →
    </a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
